<p sourcefile="articles/Perspective.md" sourcestartlinenumber="7" sourceendlinenumber="8">Enter the name of the perspective in its textbox and select its default measure in the Default Measure dropdown.<br>
<img src="https://varigencecom.blob.core.windows.net/images-mistdocumentation-editoroverviews/Perspective2.png" alt="Perspective Column" sourcefile="articles/Perspective.md" sourcestartlinenumber="8" sourceendlinenumber="8"></p>
<p sourcefile="articles/Perspective.md" sourcestartlinenumber="10" sourceendlinenumber="11">Select cube objects in the treeview to include them in the perspective.<br>
